REQ-0-DDLN-SWH-006 Change impact tracing
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The RMT SHALL be able to generate a list of all requirements changed between
 checked in versions of the project's documentation, for use as input to
 the high-to-low and low-to-high tracing functions.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Rationale: certification authority must be able to see the changes that
 happened in a period of time, e.g.
 between two successive audits.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Parents: REQ-0-DDLN-SYS-002
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Verification: Test.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Safety Impact: None.
\begin_inset Note Note
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
/req
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

