REQ-0-DDLN-SWH-007 Change history tracing
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The RMT SHALL be able to generate a list of all changelists that touched
 the definition or implementation of a given set of requirements, and the
 corresponding lists of Problem Reports that these changelists belong to.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Rationale: certification authority must be able to verify that the implementatio
n of each requirement followed the appropriate process.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Parents: REQ-0-DDLN-SYS-003
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Verification: Test.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Safety Impact: None
