REQ-0-DDLN-SWH-010 Output filtering
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The requirement sets of all the above outputs SHALL be filterable by regular
 expressions on the contents.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Rationale: to be of use in daily routine, the tool should allow quick querying
 by developers.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Parents: REQ-0-DDLN-SYS-005
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
